  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/d22d937537770452aef8b9f458ce9bfa.poster.avif?t=1755198091\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/d22d937537770452aef8b9f458ce9bfa.webm?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/d22d937537770452aef8b9f458ce9bfa.mp4?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CONTAINMENT CORP INC.</strong> is a co-op survival horror game for 1 - 4 players. Contain the anomaly and exterminate enemies in the zone. This is your chance to fight back!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>DO YOU HAVE WHAT IT TAKES?</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1-4 PLAYER ONLINE CO-OP</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of your operative in this unique online co-op survival game where you must work together to clear the infected zone and trap the otherworldly anomaly. For science.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SINGLE PLAYER MODE AVAILABLE</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Enjoy Containment Corp Inc. solo if that is more your style. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TOOL AND WEAPONS</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     You don't have to hide this time. Use your tools and weapons to fight back while gathering       evidence to capture the correct anomaly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/e001a73cf173da7872216ed17a53053a.poster.avif?t=1755198091\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/e001a73cf173da7872216ed17a53053a.webm?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/e001a73cf173da7872216ed17a53053a.mp4?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>TAKE ON THE EXTRACTION ZONE TOGETHER!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each of the <strong>4 large maps</strong> has its own special challenge and layout to learn. Discover unique secrets per map. Don't clip out. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>COMPLETE BONUS OBJECTIVES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each deployment will have its own unique set of extra challenges you can complete for more of a payout at the end of a successful mission.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>COLLECT LOOT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find rare items to be traded for money, and customizable cosmetics to change your suit and weapon appearances.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>REPLAYABILITY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each map has at least 4 unique zones you must learn to complete the objective. These maps are big, so take your time to learn them.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MULTIPLAYER FEATURES</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Make use of our in-game positional voice chat! Bring your friends to help you conquer the        zones. Or leave them behind as bait, your choice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/4cc2484d7a1778e690f8fb71ab7a08d5.poster.avif?t=1755198091\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/4cc2484d7a1778e690f8fb71ab7a08d5.webm?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/4cc2484d7a1778e690f8fb71ab7a08d5.mp4?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>EARLY ACCESS INFO</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PEER TO PEER (P2P)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our game utilizes a peer to peer system for online play, so keep that in mind!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OUR PLANS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a team of only 2 people, we are really proud of Containment Corp. But we always want to add more. Choosing to release the game as early access allows us to continually add new maps, events, and features as time goes on. If you choose to support us during early access, we thank you immensely.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/56b85634b66f58901232c2d2a589600d.poster.avif?t=1755198091\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/56b85634b66f58901232c2d2a589600d.webm?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/56b85634b66f58901232c2d2a589600d.mp4?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/d22d937537770452aef8b9f458ce9bfa.poster.avif?t=1755198091\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/d22d937537770452aef8b9f458ce9bfa.webm?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/d22d937537770452aef8b9f458ce9bfa.mp4?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CONTAINMENT CORP INC.</strong> is a co-op survival horror game for 1 - 4 players. Contain the anomaly and exterminate enemies in the zone. This is your chance to fight back!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>DO YOU HAVE WHAT IT TAKES?</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1-4 PLAYER ONLINE CO-OP</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of your operative in this unique online co-op survival game where you must work together to clear the infected zone and trap the otherworldly anomaly. For science.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SINGLE PLAYER MODE AVAILABLE</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Enjoy Containment Corp Inc. solo if that is more your style. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TOOL AND WEAPONS</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     You don't have to hide this time. Use your tools and weapons to fight back while gathering       evidence to capture the correct anomaly!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea