4cc2484d7a1778e690f8fb71ab7a08d5.poster.avif?t=1755198091\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/4cc2484d7a1778e690f8fb71ab7a08d5.webm?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/4cc2484d7a1778e690f8fb71ab7a08d5.mp4?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>EARLY ACCESS INFO</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PEER TO PEER (P2P)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our game utilizes a peer to peer system for online play, so keep that in mind!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OUR PLANS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a team of only 2 people, we are really proud of Containment Corp. But we always want to add more. Choosing to release the game as early access allows us to continually add new maps, events, and features as time goes on. If you choose to support us during early access, we thank you immensely.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/56b85634b66f58901232c2d2a589600d.poster.avif?t=1755198091\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/56b85634b66f58901232c2d2a589600d.webm?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2902580/extras/56b85634b66f58901232c2d2a589600d.mp4?t=1755198091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
